<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="w-full min-h-screen bg-zinc-900 text-white p-10">
        <p class="text-4xl mb-10">Welcome to <span class="text-yellow-500 text-5xl">PostHub!</span> Sign up today to join our vibrant community. Create, share, and explore captivating posts from users around the world. Register now to start your journey with us and become part of an ever-growing network of <span class="text-pink-500">storytellers</span> and <span class="text-red-500">creators</span>.</p>
        <h3 class="text-3xl mb-5">Create Account</h3>
        <form action="/register" method="post">
            <input class="px-3 py-2 outline-none rounded-md bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="text" name="username" placeholder="username">
            <input class="px-3 py-2 outline-none rounded-md bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="text" name="name" placeholder="name">
            <input class="px-3 py-2 outline-none rounded-md bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="email" name="email" placeholder="email">
            <input class="px-3 py-2 outline-none rounded-md bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="number" name="age" placeholder="age">
            <input class="px-3 py-2 outline-none rounded-md bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="password" name="password" placeholder="password">
            <input class="px-3 py-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-md" type="submit" value="Create Account">
        </form>
        <p class="mt-5">Already Registered? <a class="text-blue-500" href="/login">login</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>